item.title: About
item.description: About Page About the Workshop Meet your instructors and learn about our mission at the Ali Forney Center - 307 W 38th St FL 3. Hosted by: Calyx Padgett and Unity Works. Instructor’s Bio: Calyx brings expertise from a Computer Science background at Rose-Hulman and personal insights from the cybersecurity field, aiming to empower individuals with the knowledge to protect their digital lives. About Ali Forney Center: Dedicated to LGBTQ+ youth, the center provides a safe space for learning and personal growth.
